[[[description]]]
This is a shortcut macro that expands a string literal to itself and its size (including the NUL byte character). It must only be used with string literals, and is generally only used for argument passing to functions that expect a string and its respective length.

More typically, the [ZEND_STRL](https://phpinternals.net/docs/zend_strl) macro will be wanted.

